CREATE TABLE orders (order_id INT PRIMARY KEY, customer_id INT, total_amount DECIMAL(10, 2), order_date TIMESTAMP, FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES customers(customer_id));</t><s>select customers.name, orders.total_amount from customers left join orders on customers.customer_id = orders.customer_id;</s>

CREATE TABLE orders (order_id INT PRIMARY KEY, customer_id INT, total_amount DECIMAL(10, 2), order_date TIMESTAMP, FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES customers(customer_id));</t><s>select customers.name, orders.total_amount from customers join orders on customers.customer_id = orders.customer_id or orders.total_amount > 100;</s>

    customer_name TEXT,
    email TEXT,
    address TEXT
);

    product_name TEXT,
    price DECIMAL,
    category TEXT

    customer_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount DECIMAL
);

    order_item_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    order_id INT,
    product_id INT,
    quantity INT,
    total_price DECIMAL
);


CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name TEXT,
    price DECIMAL,
    category TEXT
);

    customer_name STRING,
    email STRING,
    address STRING
);


CREATE TABLE categories (
    category_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name STRING
);


CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name STRING,
    price DECIMAL,
    category STRING
);


CREATE TABLE reviews (
    review_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id UUID,
    customer_id UUID,
    rating INT,
    review_text TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id UUID,
    product_id UUID,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE
);
</t><s>SELECT * FROM customers;</s>

    product_id UUID,
    customer_id UUID,
    rating INT,
    review_text TEXT
);

);

    customer_id UUID,
    product_id UUID,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE
);

    product_id UUID,

    review_text TEXT
);

    customer_name STRING,
    email STRING,
    address STRING
);


CREATE TABLE categories (
    category_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name STRING
);


CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name STRING,
    price DECIMAL,
    category STRING
);


CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id UUID,
    product_id UUID,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE
);


CREATE TABLE reviews (
    review_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id UUID,
    customer_id UUID,
    rating INT,
    review_text TEXT
);
</t><s>SELECT customer_id, product_id, quantity FROM orders;</s>

    customer_name STRING,
    email STRING,
    address STRING
);


CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id UUID,
    product_id UUID,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE
);


CREATE TABLE categories (
    category_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name STRING
);


CREATE TABLE reviews (
    review_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id UUID,
    customer_id UUID,
    rating INT,
    review_text TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name STRING,
    price DECIMAL,
    category STRING
);
</t><s>SELECT * FROM categories;</s>

    product_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,

    product_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name STRING,
    price DECIMAL,
    category STRING
);


CREATE TABLE reviews (
    review_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id UUID,
    customer_id UUID,
    rating INT,
    review_text TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name STRING,
    email STRING,
    address STRING
);


CREATE TABLE categories (
    category_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name STRING
);


CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id UUID,
    product_id UUID,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE
);

    review_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id UUID,
    customer_id UUID,
    rating INT,
    review_text TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name STRING,
    price DECIMAL,
    category STRING
);


CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id UUID,
    product_id UUID,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE
);


CREATE TABLE categories (
    category_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name STRING
);


CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name STRING,
    email STRING,
    address STRING
);

    customer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name STRING,
    email STRING,
    address STRING
);


CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name STRING,
    price DECIMAL,
    category STRING
);


CREATE TABLE categories (
    category_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name STRING
);


CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id UUID,
    product_id UUID,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE
);


CREATE TABLE reviews (
    review_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id UUID,
    customer_id UUID,
    rating INT,
    review_text TEXT
);

    customer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name STRING,
    email STRING,
    address STRING
);


CREATE TABLE reviews (
    review_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id UUID,
    customer_id UUID,
    rating INT,
    review_text TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name STRING,
    price DECIMAL,
    category STRING
);


CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id UUID,
    product_id UUID,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE
);


CREATE TABLE categories (
    category_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name STRING
);

    product_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name STRING,
    price DECIMAL,
    category STRING
);


CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id UUID,
    product_id UUID,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE
);


CREATE TABLE reviews (
    review_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id UUID,
    customer_id UUID,
    rating INT,
    review_text TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE categories (
    category_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name STRING
);


CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name STRING,
    email STRING,
    address STRING
);

    order_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id UUID,
    product_id UUID,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE
);


CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name STRING,
    email STRING,
    address STRING
);


CREATE TABLE categories (
    category_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name STRING
);


CREATE TABLE reviews (
    review_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id UUID,
    customer_id UUID,
    rating INT,
    review_text TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name STRING,
    price DECIMAL,
    category STRING
);

    order_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id UUID,
    product_id UUID,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE
);


CREATE TABLE reviews (
    review_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id UUID,
    customer_id UUID,
    rating INT,
    review_text TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name STRING,
    price DECIMAL,
    category STRING
);


CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name STRING,
    email STRING,
    address STRING
);


CREATE TABLE categories (
    category_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name STRING
);

    category_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name STRING
);


CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id UUID,
    product_id UUID,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE
);


CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name STRING,
    email STRING,
    address STRING
);


CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name STRING,
    price DECIMAL,
    category STRING
);


CREATE TABLE reviews (
    review_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id UUID,
    customer_id UUID,
    rating INT,
    review_text TEXT
);

    review_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id UUID,
    customer_id UUID,
    rating INT,
    review_text TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name STRING,
    email STRING,
    address STRING
);


CREATE TABLE categories (
    category_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name STRING
);


CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id UUID,
    product_id UUID,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE
);


CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name STRING,
    price DECIMAL,
    category STRING
);

    review_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id UUID,
    customer_id UUID,

    review_text TEXT
);

);

    category STRING
);

);

    product_name STRING,
    price DECIMAL,
    category STRING
);


CREATE TABLE reviews (
    review_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id UUID,
    customer_id UUID,
    rating INT,
    review_text TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id UUID,
    product_id UUID,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE
);

    customer_id UUID,
    product_id UUID,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE
);

    product_id UUID,
    customer_id UUID,
    rating INT,
    review_text TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id UUID,
    product_id UUID,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE
);


CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name STRING,
    price DECIMAL,
    category STRING
);


CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name STRING,
    email STRING,
    address STRING
);


CREATE TABLE categories (
    category_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name STRING
);

    category_name STRING
);


CREATE TABLE reviews (
    review_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id UUID,
    customer_id UUID,
    rating INT,
    review_text TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name STRING,
    email STRING,
    address STRING
);


CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id UUID,
    product_id UUID,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE
);


CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name STRING,
    price DECIMAL,
    category STRING
);
</t><s>SELECT category_id, category_name FROM categories;</s>

    customer_id UUID,
    product_id UUID,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE
);

    customer_name STRING,
    email STRING,
    address STRING
);


CREATE TABLE reviews (
    review_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id UUID,
    customer_id UUID,
    rating INT,
    review_text TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name STRING,
    price DECIMAL,
    category STRING
);

    category_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name STRING
);


CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name STRING,
    email STRING,
    address STRING
);


CREATE TABLE reviews (
    review_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id UUID,
    customer_id UUID,
    rating INT,
    review_text TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id UUID,
    product_id UUID,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE
);


CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name STRING,
    price DECIMAL,
    category STRING
);

    customer_name STRING,
    email STRING,
    address STRING
);


CREATE TABLE reviews (
    review_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id UUID,
    customer_id UUID,
    rating INT,
    review_text TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id UUID,
    product_id UUID,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE
);


CREATE TABLE categories (
    category_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name STRING
);


CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name STRING,
    price DECIMAL,
    category STRING
);

    customer_id UUID,
    product_id UUID,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE
);


CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name STRING,
    price DECIMAL,
    category STRING
);


CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name STRING,
    email STRING,
    address STRING
);


CREATE TABLE reviews (
    review_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id UUID,
    customer_id UUID,
    rating INT,
    review_text TEXT
);

    product_id UUID,
    customer_id UUID,
    rating INT,
    review_text TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name STRING,
    email STRING,
    address STRING
);


CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id UUID,
    product_id UUID,
    quantity INT,
    order_date DATE
);


CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name STRING,
    price DECIMAL,
    category STRING
);


CREATE TABLE categories (
    category_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name STRING
);
</t><s>SELECT product_name, price FROM products WHERE category = 'Electronics';</s>
